data.description: Beautiful home located in Fairfield Subdivision. Enjoy resort style living in your own neighborhood! This home boast hardwood floors on main, large dining room, large living room with stone fireplace, and well appointed kitchen with an eat in area. Also, off the main living area you have a nice large well built deck to enjoy those nice Georgia weather days! Upstairs has 3 bedrooms with a bonus/bedroom for a total of 4 possible bedrooms! This home has a completely finished 1 bedroom/1 bath suite that includes a kitchen and stackable laundry unit! This home also just had a brand new roof put on in February! Don't let this one get away!
